metadata.name: $AINT$ CLXX
metadata.description:
$AINT 170, Created by [BasqKek.](https://twitter.com/BasqKek)

$AINT$ is Dr. $uss's genesis body of work. I-CLXIV (1-169) can be found on the STX blockchain (a programing/web3 layer for BTC) here on [gamma.io.](https://gamma.io/collections/aint)

ABOUT: $AINT$ is a first of its kind, 777 piece collaborative collection that blurs the lines of portraiture, pfps, memeography and fine art. Working with top artistic talent around the world, the $AINT$ collective Seize The Memes and Themes of our zeitgeist.
